{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idebecd1d2-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s40103"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"40103"},"text":"§ 40103.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Cooperation with other agencies on aeronautics activities","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Administrator shall coordinate, as appropriate, the Administration’s aeronautics activities with relevant programs in the Department of Transportation, the Department of Defense, the Department of Commerce, and the Department of Homeland Security, including the activities of the Next Generation Air Transportation System Joint Planning and Development Office established under section 709 of the Vision 100—Century of Aviation Reauthorization Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/176"},"text":"Public Law 108–176","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s40101"},"text":"49 U.S.C. 40101","children":[],"tail":" note)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idebecd1d3-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/314/s3"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–314, § 3","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/3379"},"text":"124 Stat. 3379","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idebecd1d4-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idebecd1d5-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:table","attrib":{"width":"50%","id":"idebecd1d6-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:colgroup","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:col","attrib":{},"te